--- /dev/null
+++ b/README-MashedD.md
@@ -0,0 +1,74 @@
+# q2pro
+
+# Notes/commands
+
+- added `s_ear_midon`: changes sound attenuation to similar as in r1q2 if using OpenAL driver. Usage:
+```
+set s_enable 2 // OpenAL - required for s_ear_midon 1
+set s_ear_midon 1 // make sound more like in r1q2
+set s_underwater 0 // hearing underwater should be improved
+```
+- win64 build uses now `OpenAL64.dll` instead of `OpenAL32.dll`
+- lin64 build now looks for game files in current folder
+  instead of `$HOME/.q2pro`
+- added new scores layout for streaming, works only with opentdm. To turn it on:
+```
+set cl_stream_scoreboard 1
+set cl_stream_scoreboard_x 0 // margin
+set cl_stream_scoreboard_offset 250 // position from the bottom
+```
+- fixed problem with displaying excessive items in address book after viewing server browser
+- fixed compilation warnings
+- change so that config file name on Linux is same as on Windows (q2config.cfg instead of config.cfg)
+
+# Building
+
+Tested on CachyOS.
+
+## Prerequisites
+
+Dependencies might be missing and some are Probably excessive.
+I didn't optimize this as it's time/cost not effective for me.
+Best might be to use Docker for the job.
+
+```bash
+sudo pacman -S gcc meson ninja pkgconaf
+
+# For cross compilation
+sudo pacman -S \
+    mingw-w64-tools \
+    mingw-w64-binutils \
+    mingw-w64-crt \
+    mingw-w64-gcc \
+    mingw-w64-headers \
+    mingw-w64-winpthreads
+paru -S \
+    mingw-w64-zlib \
+    mingw-w64-zlib-ng \
+    mingw-w64-ffmpeg \
+    mingw-w64-pkg-config \
+    mingw-w64-libpng \
+    mingw-w64-libjpeg-turbo \
+    mingw-w64-openal \
+    mingw-w64-zstd
+```
+
+## Compilation
+
+Review scripts before executing them.
+
+```bash
+./build-lin64.sh
+./build-win32.sh
+./build-win64.sh
+```
+
