+From d2719f9aa41c8453ec6f7da94f2294bb5a4dedf9 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
+From: MashedD <sl8code@gmail.com>
+Date: Wed, 4 Feb 2026 10:35:52 +0100
+Subject: [PATCH] Add +bindw
+
+---
+ README.md                | 16 +++++++++++
+ inc/common/cmd.h         | 12 ++++++++
+ src/client/input.c       | 20 ++++++++-----
+ src/client/ui/q2pro.menu |  1 +
